Package: CNHplus
Title: Copy Number Heterogeneity with the Non-negativity Constraint Imposed on the Absolute Copy Number Profile of Tumor
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marian Grendar
Maintainer: Marian Grendar  <marian.grendar@uniba.sk>
Description: Finds the tumor purity and the tumor ploidy for which Copy Number Heterogeneity is minimal by searching over grid, while imposing the non-negativity constraint on the recovered absolute copy number profile.
